    Connection, RMIConnectionInterface, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class RMIConnection
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements RMIConnectionInterface, Connection
    Implementation of a connection between server and client using RMI protocol This class communicates directly with RMIClientInterface.
